  "title": "Basic $8900 ►Business Development Manager (Logistics/Hunter)",
  "description": "<p>Brief Summary:</p><ul><li><p>Basic $5500 - $8900 + $1100 Transport Allowance</p></li><li><p>Mon to Fri: 8.30am - 6.00pm</p></li><li><p>Location: Greenwich</p></li><li><p>Permanent Role + VB + 14AL</p></li></ul><p>Job Responsibilities:</p><ul><li><p>Responsible for new business and new market development of an assigned business division in Singapore & Malaysia.</p></li><li><p>Develop & execute strategic plans for new business & markets growth.</p></li><li><p>Monitor and evaluate market trends for timely reactions to market.</p></li><li><p>Achieve sales targets.</p></li></ul><p>Job Requirements:</p><ul><li><p><strong>2 – 3 years in a hunter role</strong> with proven success securing new clients.</p></li><li><p>Experience with tenders, RFQs, pricing, trade lanes, and account management.</p></li><li><p>Degree in Marketing, Sales, or related field.</p></li></ul><p>For consideration, kindly submit your CV by clicking “APPLY NOW” or TEXT <a href=\"tel:+65 9422 1220\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">+65 9422 1220</a> for confidential discussion.</p><p>*Only shortlisted candidates would be notified*</p><p>MTC Consulting Pte Ltd | 15C7752</p><p>EA. Registration No.: R22111807 | Yap Teng Hui</p>",
